Name: White Pine Arrow Shafts
Description: They're like skinny, baby logs. Feathers can be attached to the end.
gatherString: You make $ arrow shafts from the white pine wood.

Name: Headless White Pine Arrows
Description: Skinny, wobbly sticks with feathers on the end. Add some arrow heads to make arrows.
